Book Description: With the help of Duct Tape Discovery Workshop, you'll learn the techniques to make working with duct tape easy and stylish. Hosting a get together at your place? Make a set of duct tape coasters and stemware tags to match your party's theme! Need a gift for one of your gal pals? Fashion a set of feather earrings, wrap it in a set of masu boxes and make a matching duct tape card. Want to cheer up a drab room or desk? Create a colorful mosaic frame! The possibilities for duct tape crafting are endless and with these unexpected projects, you'll use duct tape in ways you never imagined.
